Interface DispatchAsync

All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractDispatchAsync, SecureDispatchAsync, StandardDispatchAsync
public interface DispatchAsync

This is an asynchronous equivalent of the Dispatch interface on the server side. The reason it exists is because GWT currently can't correctly handle having generic method templates in method signatures (eg. <A> A create( Class type ))
